Question: The combined images include at least one standing adult wild pig and at least one standing baby piglet with distinctive brown and beige striped fur.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3sgYUa8598s/hqdefault.jpg

Right image URL: http://www.dw.com/image/6685138_7.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a standing adult wild pig in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a standing adult wild pig in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a standing baby piglet with distinctive brown and beige striped fur in the image?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a standing baby piglet with distinctive brown and beige striped fur in the image?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} or {ANSWER1}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} or {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
